\f0\fs24 \cf0 Welcome to {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://metissian.com/projects/macosx/subversion/"}}{\fldrslt VDrift}}, a cross-platform, open source driving simulation made with drift racing in mind. The driving physics engine was recently re-written from scratch but was inspired and owes much to the Vamos physics engine. It is released under the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html"}}{\fldrslt GNU General Public License (GPL) v3}}. It is currently available for {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.linux.org/"}}{\fldrslt Linux}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.apple.com/macosx/"}}{\fldrslt Mac OS X}} and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://windows.microsoft.com/en-US/windows/home"}}{\fldrslt Windows}}. \
For more information visit the website: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://vdrift.net"}}{\fldrslt vdrift.net}} or the wiki: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wiki.vdrift.net/Main_Page"}}{\fldrslt wiki.vdrift.net/Main_Page}}\
\

\fs28 \ul Binary Install
\fs24 \ulnone \

\b Prerequisites
\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}See {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wiki.vdrift.net/Hardware_requirements"}}{\fldrslt Hardware requirements}} and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wiki.vdrift.net/Software_requirements"}}{\fldrslt Software requirements}}.\
{\listtext	\'95	}VDrift requires {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.apple.com/macosx/"}}{\fldrslt Mac OS X}} 10.4 "Tiger" or higher.\
\pard\pardeftab720
\cf0 \

\b Installing
\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Download the latest VDrift release for Mac OS X from the link on the homepage at {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://vdrift.net"}}{\fldrslt vdrift.net}} or {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://sourceforge.net/projects/vdrift/files/vdrift/"}}{\fldrslt SourceForge}}.\
{\listtext	\'95	}If it doesn't automatically open, double click the ''vdrift-mac-yyyy-mm-dd.dmg'' file (probably in your download folder).\
{\listtext	\'95	}Drag or copy all the files and folders from the resulting mounted disk image named 
\i VDrift
\i0  to your 
\i Applications
\i0  folder.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Double-click the 
\i VDrift
\i0  application now found in your 
\i Applications
\i0  folder.\
\pard\pardeftab720
\cf0 \

